text: Tuberodiadelia tubericollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the only species in the genus Tuberodiadelia. It was described by Breuning in 1957.Biolib.cz - Tuberodiadelia tubericollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 1957
